description.narrative: The Support to National Malaria Programme aims to assist the Nigerian government in malaria prevention and treatment through improvements in capacity, project planning and coordination, drug and net distribution, and demand creation. Working alongside DFID Nigeria at the federal and state level, Malaria Consortium is implementing SuNMaP2 in up to six states. The project is funded by DFID/UKaid. [Nigeria]
